description: The Monterey Coffee Table combines the Coastal and Farmhouse styles in to fashionable and functional table. Constructed from solid Pine and finished in a Black base and Brown Top. Two (2) well sized drawers allow for plenty of storage space for TV controllers, magazines, puzzles, board games and other items. Each drawer is designed to be pulled through in order to access from either side. Antique pewter finished hardware, miter cuts on the top, framed drawers adds an extra element of detail to the collection. Hidden caster wheels are included allowing you to move the table to different positions which is perfect for a motion sofa or chair. Assembled product dimensions: 50" W x 28" D x 19" H. Product materials: Solid wood - New Zealand Pine. Easy assembly required. Made in Vietnam.
